{"tid":961953,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"好心借錢竟被殺　俄國女高生半裸遭棄屍河中島","createTime":"2018-12-30T13:36:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-31T07:13:14.000Z","uid":130626,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"c63d1503877afce01e532c90d2835a6a15a8630f","tid":961953,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-30T13:36:07.000Z","msg":"俄羅斯下烏金斯克（Nizhneudinsk）一名女高中生，日前出門後就沒回家，失蹤整整8天後，被人發現她半裸陳屍在一處河中島的灌木叢中。警方調查發現，兇手竟是死者的高中同學，只因還不出約3.2萬元台幣的借款，竟對她痛下殺手！主嫌的媽媽為了救子，還當起搬運工將屍體送到河中島上棄屍。<br />\n《太陽報》報導，17歲女高中生古妮爾（Gyunel Dadashova），日前找女性友人維多利亞（Viktoria）陪她一起到嫌犯瑪寇（Igor Marko，17歲）家中討錢，沒想到古妮爾進去後就被瑪寇和其15歲同夥謝爾蓋（Sergei）砍殺致死。<br />\n維多利亞供稱，她當時在門外等待，但當門再度打開時，只見古妮爾倒臥血泊中，瑪寇和謝爾蓋恐嚇她不准說出去，否則下場就會跟古妮爾一樣，當時她嚇得什麼都不敢說。<br />\n瑪寇和謝爾蓋則將古妮爾的屍體扔進地窖中。2天後，瑪寇的媽媽打掃時意外發現血手套，詢問後得知兒子殺了人，她非但沒有帶兒子去自首，反而協助脫下古妮爾身上的血衣，運屍埋至偏僻處。<br />\n瑪寇的媽媽供稱自己單純是為了拯救愛子，希望兒子和其朋友不要變成兇手，才決定這麼做。瑪寇和謝爾蓋現已遭法辦，若被定罪，將會面臨8年至20年徒刑。瑪寇媽媽的刑責則尚待審判結果出爐。（即時新聞中心／綜合報導）<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20181230/640_a1e601246674c5f781a1661d4948d692.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20181230%2F640_a1e601246674c5f781a1661d4948d692.jpg&h=cd9649a5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20181230/640_13c3b6ea4cd5bbb5065faafe350dff1e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20181230%2F640_13c3b6ea4cd5bbb5065faafe350dff1e.jpg&h=9be84ebb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n古妮爾（圖）命喪男同學之手。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20181230/640_b1f13da237768ea4bd5e09e1d6f5b7a8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20181230%2F640_b1f13da237768ea4bd5e09e1d6f5b7a8.jpg&h=94bebc95&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n主嫌瑪寇的媽媽（圖）竟幫兒子運屍去埋。"},{"pid":"ff73f341635881e8c20f369e72b4b09a19d4f618","tid":961953,"uid":155818,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-30T13:36:32.000Z","msg":"媽媽<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b482632feef9f0fa7056945cc9efe38e619e5cd7","tid":961953,"uid":161190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-30T13:37:35.000Z","msg":"Rip"},{"pid":"0cf0cfe646e3da2e5271af2a767229a55a5a680b","tid":961953,"uid":130626,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"ff73f341635881e8c20f369e72b4b09a19d4f618","tid":961953,"uid":155818,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-30T13:36:32.000Z","msg":"媽媽<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-31T07:13:14.000Z","msg":"你有冇咁痴線<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}